column4: Culture – CUL2 Self-Awareness – students will be able to articulate an understanding of themselves as part of culture(s) with rich historical perspectives through the study of works of culture.
column11: Advanced: Demonstrates a sophisticated and multi-layered  ability to articulate an understanding of  themselves as part of culture(s) with rich  historical perspectives through the study of  works of culture.
column13: Proficient: Demonstrates an advanced ability to articulate an understanding of themselves as part of culture(s) with rich historical perspectives through the study of works of culture.
column15: Progressing: Demonstrates a basic ability to articulate an understanding of themselves as part of culture(s) with rich historical perspectives through the study of works of culture.
column17: Beginning: Demonstrates a partial ability to articulate an  understanding of themselves as part of culture(s) with rich historical perspectives through the study of works of culture.
column19: Unsatisfactory: Demonstrates little ability to articulate an understanding of themselves as part of culture(s) with rich historical perspectives through the study of works of culture.
